            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 490,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7600,
            "LocalizeKR": "여전히 얼빠진 표정이네.",
            "LocalizeJP": "相変わらず、間抜けな顔。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 500,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4550,
            "LocalizeKR": "글쎄……\n누군가가 말했었지.",
            "LocalizeJP": "まあね……\nある人が言ってたんだ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 510,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13150,
            "LocalizeKR": "휴식을 취하는 건,\n일하는 것만큼이나, 아니,\n그 이상으로 중요하다, 고.",
            "LocalizeJP": "休息を取る事は、\n働くのと同じぐらい、いや、\nそれ以上に大事だ、って。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 520,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11000,
            "LocalizeKR": "후후, 우수한 참모는\n타인의 금언도 제대로\n기억해두는 법이야.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ふふ、優秀な参謀は、\n他人の金言もちゃんと\n覚えているんだよ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 530,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7150,
            "LocalizeKR": "봐, 선생님에게\n추천하고 싶은 책이\n이렇게나 많아.",
            "LocalizeJP": "みて、先生に\nオススメしたい本、\nこんなにたくさんあるの。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 540,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8900,
            "LocalizeKR": "아, 그 전에……\n방 청소랑, 녹차 한잔.\n부탁해도 될까?",
            "LocalizeJP": "あ、その前に……\n部屋の掃除と、緑茶を\n一杯、お願いできるかな。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 550,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10950,
            "LocalizeKR": "본인이 직접 말한 거잖아?\n거절하지는 않겠지?",
            "LocalizeJP": "自分で言いだしたことでしょう？\n断ったりしないよね？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 560,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8000,
            "LocalizeKR": "그래……\n당신은 그런 사람이었지.\n…알고 있었지만.",
            "LocalizeJP": "そうだ…あんたって\nそういう人だった…\n知ってたけど。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 570,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8500,
            "LocalizeKR": "뭐, 상관없나.\n나 키류 키쿄는 모처럼의\n기회를 발로 차진 않아.",
            "LocalizeJP": "まぁいっか。\n桐生キキョウは、\nせっかくの機会を棒に\n振る真似はしない。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10083,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008301,
            "DisplayOrder": 580,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12550,
            "LocalizeKR": "전력을 다해\n응석을 부릴 테니,\n각오하도록 해…… 후후.",
            "LocalizeJP": "全身全霊で甘えるから、\n覚悟しててね……ふふ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          }
        ],
